    {
      "id": "ex-li-1",
      "type": "listen",
      "skill": "listening",
      "prompt": "Listen to the property visit. What is praised?",
      "audio": "audio/b2.1/unit-05-qualification/listen-1.mp3",
      "transcript": "Le salon est très lumineux, et la salle de bains, dont le carrelage est neuf, vient d'être rénovée.",
      "options": [
        {
          "id": "a",
          "text": "A bright living room and a newly renovated bathroom"
        },
        {
          "id": "b",
          "text": "A dark living room with old tiles"
        },
        {
          "id": "c",
          "text": "A spacious kitchen with a leather sofa"
        }
      ],
      "correct": [
        "a"
      ],
      "explanation": "lumineux + salle de bains rénovée (dont le carrelage est neuf — relative with dont)."
    },
    {
      "id": "ex-rd-1",
      "type": "read",
      "skill": "reading",
      "prompt": "Read the listing and answer both questions.",
      "passageFr": "À LOUER — Appartement de trois pièces, lumineux et spacieux, dans un immeuble ancien entièrement rénové. Cuisine équipée avec machine à laver, salle de bains neuve. Quartier animé dans lequel commerces et écoles se font à pied. Loyer : 980 € charges comprises. Les locataires actuels quittent le logement fin août.",
      "passageEn": "FOR RENT — Three-room apartment, bright and spacious, in a fully renovated old building. Fitted kitchen with washing machine, brand-new bathroom. Lively neighbourhood where shops and schools are within walking distance. Rent: €980 including utilities. The current tenants leave at the end of August.",
      "questions": [
        {
          "id": "q1",
          "prompt": "What does the rent include?",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "a",
              "text": "Utilities (charges)"
            },
            {
              "id": "b",
              "text": "Furniture"
            },
            {
              "id": "c",
              "text": "Parking and a cellar"
            }
          ],
          "correct": [
            "a"
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "q2",
          "prompt": "When do the current tenants leave?",
          "options": [
            {
              "id": "a",
              "text": "At the end of August"
            },
            {
              "id": "b",
              "text": "Immediately"
            },
            {
              "id": "c",
              "text": "The listing doesn't say"
            }
          ],
          "correct": [
            "a"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
